    mc "是啊，确实如此--压力大、乱成一团，但很充实。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:230
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_2e8ac8f7:

    # mc "We actually just finished renovating our studio."
    mc "我们其实刚完成工作室的翻新。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:232
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_688120ef:

    # mc "We're actually doing some renovations to turn it into a proper studio."
    mc "我们正在做一些改造，想把它变成一个真正像样的工作室。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:234
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_7c16c5aa:

    # mc "We've started laying the groundwork for a real, proper studio."
    mc "我们已经开始为一个货真价实的专业工作室打基础了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:237
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_e899127c:

    # mc "Sometimes it feels impossible. I'll be the first to admit it's pretty ambitious."
    mc "有时候感觉这一切遥不可及。我得承认，这个目标有点远大。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:238
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_29e6f04e:

    # mc "But Stacy is a huge help. She's unstoppable when she sets her mind on something."
    mc "但史黛西帮了大忙。她一旦下定决心，就没有办不成的事。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:241
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_bdad4d9e:

    # mes "I didn't get to know her that well, but she sounds like a girl of great determination."
    mes "我和她不算很熟，但听起来她是个很有决断力的女孩。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:243
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_dfc1c7fb:

    # mc "She's the reason we've gotten this far. I'm the eye candy and jokester mostly."
    mc "我们能走到这一步全靠她。我主要负责当花瓶和讲笑话。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:246
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_b54749f3:

    # mes "And why exactly does a team of professionals need a jokester?"
    mes "什么一个专业团队需要讲笑话的人？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:248
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_f1a7154e:

    # mc "When you're painting and drywalling walls for the third day straight, it helps to have someone cracking jokes at two in the morning."
    mc "当你连续三天刷墙、钉石膏板时，凌晨两点有人讲笑话真的很解压。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:251
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_ba677a9b:

    # mes "*light laugh* I'll believe it when I see it."
    mes "*轻笑* 等我亲眼见到再说吧。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:252
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_017876c4:

    # mes "But I'm still surprised you gave up college for this."
    mes "不过你为了这个放弃学业，还是让我很意外。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:255
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_636caa35:

    # mc "For now, yeah. I might go back once the business is up and running, but I realized I was more passionate about creating something tangible than sitting in a classroom."
    mc "暂时是这样。等工作室步入正轨，我可能会回去上学。但我意识到，比起坐在教室里，我更热衷于创造实实在在的东西。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:258
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_e9eb76ee:

    # mes "Passion is good. Honestly, I've wrestled with the idea of quitting too, so many times."
    mes "有热情是好事。说实话，我也无数次想过退学。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:259
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_07ac0714:

    # mes "Classes just don't feel the same after everything that happened."
    mes "经历了这些事后，上课的感觉完全不一样了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:262
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_623a0838:

    # mes "I thought when I went to Korea, things would change. Learning would have that luster it used to have, but it didn't help."
    mes "我本来以为去了韩国，一切都会改变。学习对我而言会重新变得有吸引力，但并没有。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:263
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_d1410c59:

    # mes "Maybe it's time to set my classes aside."
    mes "也许是时候把学业放一放了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:267
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_62e926ae:

    # mc "Min, I didn't mean to make it sound like dropping out is the greatest idea in the world. It's not for everyone."
    mc "明，我可不是说退学是什么伟大的决定。它不是一个适合所有人的选择。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:268
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_a3ff538d:

    # mc "Stacy and I have definitely had our share of second thoughts. But it's what felt right for me."
    mc "我和史黛西也经常自我怀疑。但这对我来说是正确选择。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:272
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_af603402:

    # mes "I get it. Don't worry, [mcname]. It's not like I'm going to drop out tomorrow or anything."
    mes "我明白。别担心，[mcname]。我又不是说明天就退学。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:276
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_cca426f6:

    # mes "So... what's it like living with Stacy as not just your sister, but now your partner in crime and bed, so to speak?"
    mes "所以...和史黛西同居是什么感觉？现在她不仅是你妹妹，还是你的事业伙伴，嗯...某种程度上也是你的床伴？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:278
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_67bd7b07:

    # mes "So... what's it like living with your childhood friend, but now your partner in crime and bed, so to speak?"
    mes "所以...和青梅竹马同居是什么感觉？现在她不仅是你童年玩伴，还是你的事业搭档，嗯...某种程度上也是你的床伴？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:281
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_58832f50:

    # mc "*grin* It's never dull, I'll say that. We were close before, but now that we're building something together, there's this new energy."
    mc "*咧嘴笑* 一句话，永远也不会觉得无聊。我们本来就很亲密，但现在一起创业，感觉俩人的关系更有活力了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:282
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_39c46ca2:

    # mc "We're basically a couple — but she doesn't mind me being with other girls."
    mc "我们基本算是情侣--但她不介意我和其他女孩交往。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:285
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_e9f707ae:

    # mes "Wait, so she's okay with you dating around?"
    mes "等等，她居然允许你和别人约会？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:287
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_86fcb108:

    # mc "Oh yeah. Sometimes, she even pushes me to do it. She jokes about it constantly. It was a little strange at first, but it works for us."
    mc "当然。有时候她甚至主动撺掇我去。她总拿这事开玩笑。一开始有点奇怪，但我们俩都适应了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:290
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_305c750e:

    # mes "She's very unique."
    mes "她真的很特别。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:292
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_35324042:

    # mc "You can say that again."
    mc "说得太对了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:295
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_8c278614:

    # mc "I think her biggest kink is seeing me squirm in embarrassing situations that she puts me in."
    mc "我觉得她最大的情趣，就是看我被她坑进尴尬场面里扭捏挣扎。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:296
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_2b444a56:

    # mc "But hey, I love her for it, and she loves me."
    mc "但不管怎样，我爱这样的她，她也爱这样的我。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:299
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0ffd43c2:

    # mes "That's good to hear. I'm glad you're doing something that makes you happy."
    mes "真好。你找到了让自己快乐的事，真好。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:300
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_6653baef:

    # mes "But I can't help but wonder if-"
    mes "但我不禁在想，如果--"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:303
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_83d89bc9:

    # mes "Forget it."
    mes "算了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:305
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_7b252ff6:

    # mc "Come on, I know you got something on your chest, Min."
    mc "别这样，我知道你有话想说，明。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:307
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_81aef917:

    # mes "..."
    mes "..."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:309
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_1fd38f1f:

    # mc "I can't believe this. *chuckles*{w} The old Min was never shy."
    mc "真不敢相信。*轻笑*{w}以前的明可从来不会吞吞吐吐的。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:312
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_490cd4da:

    # mes "It's nothing. I just... I wonder if I messed up by not staying in touch."
    mes "没什么。只是...我在想，当初没和你保持联系，是不是错了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:314
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0ed4f6e3:

    # mc "Min, you had your reasons. We all had complicated stuff going on. Lydia, FL, Anthony... there was so much drama swirling around."
    mc "明，你有你的理由。我们当时都被一堆破事缠身。莉迪亚、性趣探测器、安东尼...各种闹剧轮番上演。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:317
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_a2f9d1d5:

    # mes "Yeah, Anthony... That was a whole other can of worms. He was controlling in his own way, and I guess it didn't help that I was already half in love with you at the time."
    mes "是啊，安东尼...那又是另一团乱麻。他用他的方式控制着我，而我当时又刚好对你有那么点好感。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:320
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_87d35c3f:

    # mct "Woah. Min was in love with me?"
    mct "等等，明居然喜欢过我？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:322
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0ebcd261:

    # mes "I mean, obviously we were just messing around, not taking it seriously. That's how I saw it."
    mes "我是说，显然我们当时只是玩玩，没当真。至少我是这么想的。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:325
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_debaba97:

    # mc "Min, for me, it wasn't just messing around. You know I cared about you. I still do. I'm sorry if I gave you the impression that it was just a fling."
    mc "明，对我来说，那不是随便玩玩。你知道我在乎过你。现在也在乎。如果我让你觉得那只是逢场作戏，我很抱歉。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:328
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_7bbda5b2:

    # mes "*quietly* We both had a lot going on back then..."
    mes "*轻声说* 我们当时都有太多烦心事..."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:329
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_1f830518:

    # mes "Then Lydia's betrayal came out, I panicked. I pulled away and went off to Korea, trying to 'find myself' or something cheesy like that."
    mes "后来莉迪亚背叛的事曝光，我慌了。我逃去了韩国，想上演‘找回自我’之类的老套剧情。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:332
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_05daebeb:

    # mc "Do you regret leaving?"
    mc "你后悔离开吗？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:335
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_adc114cd:

    # mes "I regret running away from my problems but not seeing my parents. They needed me, and maybe I needed them more than I realized."
    mes "我后悔逃避问题，但不后悔见到父母。他们需要我，或许我也许比想象中的更需要他们。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:336
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_4f247ad4:

    # mes "At least for a while."
    mes "至少有那么一段时间是这样。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:340
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_7d010a14:

    # mc "What happened?"
    mc "然后呢？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:342
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_d19c0b1c:

    # mes "My {i}loving{/i} family tried setting me up with a 'nice, respectable' suitor — who does that these days?"
    mes "我{i}亲爱的{/i}家人想给我安排一个'体面优秀'的相亲对象--都什么年代了还搞这套？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:348
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_bd02302b:

    # mes "*light laugh* Exactly. I said 'hard pass,' obviously. But it was still awkward as hell."
    mes "*轻笑* 没错。我当然当场拒绝了。但场面还是尴尬得要死。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:349
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_32ffdb67:

    # mes "*sighs* I know they meant well."
    mes "*叹气* 我知道他们是好意。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:350
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_812f8da4:

    # mes "They saw me floundering, they knew I was upset about life, and they thought, 'Oh, a stable relationship will fix everything'."
    mes "他们看我一蹶不振，知道我对生活很迷茫，就觉得‘哎呀，稳定的感情能解决一切’。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:353
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_e13edf2e:

    # mc "Too bad they didn't consider that stable also means \"happy\" something a forced setup wouldn't necessarily guarantee."
    mc "可惜他们没考虑到，‘稳定’也意味着\"幸福\"，而被迫的安排未必能带来幸福。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:356
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_d4c70379:

    # mes "Exactly."
    mes "一点没错。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:357
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_ea8a3b9b:

    # mes "So, about the studio... Is it actually a job or more of a hobby?"
    mes "说说工作室吧...这算是正经工作，还是更像业余爱好？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:361
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_a2b7ebd5:

    # mc "Oh it's a full-time job."
    mc "哦，这是全职工作。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:362
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_2b76248e:

    # mc "I mean, we only have one real client so far — a guy who specifically wanted a redhead in his short film."
    mc "虽然目前只有一个正式客户--一个着重要求红发女郎出演短片的家伙。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:363
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_017fb432:

    # mc "But it's a start."
    mc "但好歹是个开始。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:366
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_cd529352:

    # mes "Impressive. I just assumed you two were just messing around with a camera in a warehouse."
    mes "挺厉害的。我之前还以为你们只是在仓库里拿着相机瞎玩。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:371
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_c61da560:

    # mes "I find that hard to believe."
    mes "这我可不信。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:374
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_4cb19060:

    # mes "Or maybe I'm just the teensy bit jealous."
    mes "或者说，我只是有那么一点点嫉妒。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:376
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_a0809cf3:

    # mc "Hah, hard to believe that."
    mc "哈，难以想象。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:379
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_c34e8a26:

    # mes "I'm being serious. You took a risk, and it's paying off. Meanwhile, I'm just drifting."
    mes "我说真的。你敢于冒险，而且正在收获回报。而我呢，只是在随波逐流。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:382
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_8f7dfa62:

    # mc "You should come check it out sometime. When you're not busy."
    mc "有空你该来看看。等你不忙的时候。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:384
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_daf92d0e:

    # mes "Stacy wouldn't mind me poking around your big project, given our history?"
    mes "考虑到我们的过去，史黛西不会介意我掺和你们的大项目吧？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:387
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_cd42b98b:

    # mc "It won't be a problem. I'm sure, given the chance, you two would connect."
    mc "不会有问题的。我相信如果有机会，你们俩会很合得来。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:388
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_28dae137:

    # mc "You both can be super driven."
    mc "你们都是行动力超强的人。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:392
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_117f8328:

    # mes "Hmmm. I was once, wasn't I?"
    mes "嗯。我以前确实很有冲劲，对吧？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:394
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_74f72917:

    # mc "It's not gone, Min. That would be impossible."
    mc "你那份冲劲还在，明。它不可能消失。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:395
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_dfdc5f22:

    # mc "Maybe your spark is just a little sleepy, but I {i}know{/i} it's there, Min."
    mc "也许只是暂时休眠了，但我{i}知道{/i}它就在那里，明。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:398
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_340d05b0:

    # mes "You always did know how to say the right thing to make me feel better."
    mes "你总是知道说什么能让我好受些。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:401
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_75524cbb:

    # mc "If I'm being honest, half of the time, I'm winging it, hoping for the best."
    mc "说实话，多半时候我都是临场发挥，走一步算一步。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:403
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_907c5e87:

    # mes "*laughs lightly* Good to know some things never change."
    mes "*轻声笑* 还好有些东西从未改变。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:406
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_584f1b52:

    # mct "This laughter is the most genuine thing I've seen from her tonight. It's like a weight has lifted, at least momentarily."
    mct "这是今晚我见过她最真诚的笑容。仿佛有什么重担暂时卸下了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:409
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_1a27c394:

    # mes "Well, [mcname], I've got to say, I missed you. You and your silly jokes, the way you always found something goofy in every serious situation."
    mes "[mcname]，说真的，我很想你。想念你的傻笑话，想念你总能在严肃场合里找到乐子的本事。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:410
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_8d58ebd4:

    # mes "It used to drive me crazy, but now I realize how comforting it was."
    mes "以前这让我抓狂，但现在我才意识到，这有多让人安心。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:413
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_fa439270:

    # mc "Hey, that's my specialty, acting like a doofus when tension gets too high."
    mc "嘿，这就是我的特长--气氛越紧张，我越要当搞笑担当。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:417
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_6e0c7511:

    # mes "You know what, maybe I will have another drink. Or maybe not. I'm not trying to get hammered tonight."
    mes "知道吗，也许我该再来一杯。不过算了。我今晚不想喝到烂醉。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:418
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_b1765de3:

    # mes "But I feel like celebrating just a tiny bit — celebrating the fact that I'm not alone here after all."
    mes "但还是想小小庆祝一下--庆祝我终于不再觉得自己在这儿孤孤单单了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:420
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_eecfc5f3:

    # mc "We can celebrate with or without alcohol, your call. I'm good either way."
    mc "要不要喝酒随你，我都奉陪。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:424
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0139ff85:

    # mes "Let's go light on it. The last thing I need is a killer hangover with classes starting up again soon."
    mes "少喝点吧。毕竟开学在即，我可不想醉到头痛欲裂。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:426
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_7395e8c9:

    # mc "Right, you're continuing your business management program, yeah?"
    mc "对了，你还在继续修工商管理，对吧？"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:430
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_1cbc0b6d:

    # mes "Yeah. I might skip a few electives this semester to focus on the core classes, though. My head's been a mess, so I need to pace myself."
    mes "是啊。不过这学期可能会跳过几门选修课，专注核心课程。我最近脑子太乱，得调整下节奏。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:432
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_3ab8c655:

    # mc "Makes sense. Honestly, if you ever need help studying, you know where to find me."
    mc "有道理。如果你需要学习上的帮助，随时找我。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:435
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_d5239904:

    # mes "Something tells me you'd be a bigger distraction than a help."
    mes "直觉告诉我，你与其说是帮助，不如说是干扰。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:437
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_5665f6ed:

    # mc "*mock offense* Hey, I know how to tamper down my sex appeal. I'm not some out-of-control sex addict."
    mc "*假装受伤* 嘿，我知道怎么收敛魅力好吗。我又不是什么失控的色情狂。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:442
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_83991247:

    # mes "No, of course not. That's a totally normal response."
    mes "当然不是。你这反应完全正常。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:443
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_8faa0c7c:

    # mes "*teasing* Sure, sure. You'd probably show up with a camera crew and say it's for your next short film."
    mes "*调侃* 是是是。你说不定会带着你的摄影团队出现，说这是为下一部短片取材。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:447
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0ea913ae:

    # mc "Now that's an idea. \"Documenting the daily struggles of a college student dealing with a watersports addiction\". You'd star as yourself, of course, and I'd direct."
    mc "这主意不错。就叫\"记录一名大学生与‘玩水作乐’的日常挣扎\"。你当然本色出演，我当导演。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:449
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_39be139e:

    # mes "I'd watch that."
    mes "我会想看这部。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:465
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_c3ff5792:

    # mes "It's getting late. I should get going."
    mes "时候不早了，我该走了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:467
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_6abc3f73:

    # mc "Min... I'm really glad we got a chance to talk. I know you've been through hell. If there's anything I can do — anything at all — just say the word."
    mc "明...真的很高兴能和你聊聊。我知道你经历了很多。如果有任何需要--任何事--你都可以随时开口。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:470
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_0ad8d8eb:

    # mes "You've already done plenty, [mcname]."
    mes "你已经帮了我很多，[mcname]。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:471
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_4b096d8e:

    # mes "But I'll keep that in mind."
    mes "不过我会记在心里的。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:474
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_c66afb5b:

    # mes "If nothing else, I'm sure I'd enjoy drinks again. Down the line."
    mes "至少下次可以再一起喝一杯。改天吧。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:475
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_8f22e8b0:

    # mes "If you're up to it."
    mes "如果你愿意的话。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:478
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_927c1195:

    # mc "Cool, it's a deal then."
    mc "好啊，那就说定了。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:103
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_66273e86:

    # mes "*chuckles wryly* The elephant in the room."
    mes "*chuckles wryly* The elephant in the room."
    mes "*苦笑* 房间里的大象。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:219
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_9af4df5f:

    # mc "*sheepishly* Guilty as charged. The old business management program just wasn't cutting it for me."
    mc "*sheepishly* Guilty as charged. The old business management program just wasn't cutting it for me."
    mc "*不好意思地* 确实如此。之前那个工商管理专业对我来说实在不太合适。"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/mes/sm1cs-mes001.rpy:344
translate chinese sm1cs_mes001_3a955c35:

    # mc "Are you telling me you almost got a set up for an arranged marriage type date in Korea?"
    mc "Are you telling me you almost got a set up for an arranged marriage type date in Korea?"
    mc "你是说你在韩国差点被安排了相亲？"

